24:52.129 --> 24:53.680
but my uncle Julius
is an attorney

24:53.731 --> 24:54.848
and we will sue you

24:54.899 --> 24:56.149
right back.

24:56.183 --> 24:58.235
No, I don't need a night
to think about it.

25:01.522 --> 25:03.156
Look, I cannot <i>believe</i>

25:03.190 --> 25:04.491
what just happened.
Who was that?

25:04.525 --> 25:07.577
Just my useless "producer."

25:07.612 --> 25:08.695
I thought you liked him.

25:08.746 --> 25:09.696
I did.

25:09.747 --> 25:11.331
When we were in the studio.

25:11.365 --> 25:16.336
♪ Whoa-oh.

25:16.370 --> 25:17.871
I'd say let's have
another go, Mercedes,

25:17.922 --> 25:19.339
but honestly, your voice

25:19.373 --> 25:20.590
was perfection.

25:20.625 --> 25:22.292
So, let's move on
with "Lover on the DL"

25:22.326 --> 25:23.510
if we can, please.

25:23.544 --> 25:25.178
<i>Then I got a little skeptical</i>

25:25.212 --> 25:27.714
<i>when we were doing the photo</i>
<i>shoot for my CD's cover art.</i>

25:27.765 --> 25:29.883
Could you just lean forward
a bit there, Mercedes?

25:31.102 --> 25:32.269
And drop that shoulder wrap.

25:32.303 --> 25:33.937
Look, I'm not
comfortable with that,

25:33.971 --> 25:35.004
Martin.

25:35.940 --> 25:36.890
You look like a girl

25:36.941 --> 25:38.058
going to church or the prom.

25:38.109 --> 25:39.192
Not like a girl

25:39.226 --> 25:41.111
who needs to move 100,000 units

25:41.145 --> 25:43.613
just to make a minor splash
in this marketplace.

25:43.648 --> 25:45.198
This is the look.

25:45.232 --> 25:46.900
This is what I'm wearing.

25:46.951 --> 25:48.068
All right.

25:49.153 --> 25:50.870
You heard the lady.

25:50.905 --> 25:52.205
She's the boss.

25:52.239 --> 25:53.657
Now they're saying my CD

25:53.691 --> 25:55.041
is off of their
release schedule

25:55.076 --> 25:57.377
until I agree to another photo shoot.

25:57.411 --> 25:59.212
One showing more skin.

25:59.246 --> 26:00.747
What? Screw him.

26:00.798 --> 26:02.132
Oh, and he said he'd be happy

26:02.166 --> 26:03.133
to use another girl's picture.

26:03.167 --> 26:04.217
On your CD?

26:04.251 --> 26:05.752
The one that you
are singing on?

26:05.803 --> 26:06.803
Oh, hell to the no.

26:06.837 --> 26:08.338
They don't want me.

26:08.372 --> 26:09.756
They just want my voice,

26:09.807 --> 26:10.890
not my whole person.

26:10.925 --> 26:12.559
You know, it's crazy, guys.

26:12.593 --> 26:13.727
I'm going to be

26:13.761 --> 26:17.013
