is gonna be satisfied

26:20.851 --> 26:23.103
with me, Mercedes Jones.

26:23.154 --> 26:24.571
And they're crazy, and
you don't want to be

26:24.605 --> 26:25.939
in business with
people like that.

26:25.990 --> 26:27.941
