considering it, are you?

26:27.992 --> 26:30.660
I've been working on
this album for a year.

26:30.695 --> 26:32.996
I need it to come out.

26:34.448 --> 26:36.166
Look, I'm sorry, guys.

26:36.200 --> 26:37.917
I don't what I'm gonna do,

26:37.952 --> 26:40.453
but I need to talk to my mom
about this hot mess.

26:51.072 --> 26:53.524
Mom, I'm home.

26:53.558 --> 26:54.758
Hi, Artie.

26:54.776 --> 26:56.560
Yeah, hey, Artie.

26:59.647 --> 27:02.116
Guess I beat you here,
and I guess I beat

27:02.150 --> 27:04.218
