mom about your good news.

27:04.252 --> 27:07.454
Honey, why would you hide
something like that from me?

27:07.489 --> 27:09.289
So much for your lies.

27:09.324 --> 27:11.608
Your mom's completely
on board with you going

27:11.626 --> 27:13.410
to Brooklyn Film Academy,
by the way.

27:13.444 --> 27:15.245
I thought you were
a lot of things,

27:15.279 --> 27:17.114
