that I'm afraid

27:27.258 --> 27:28.809
to let you go to New York?

27:30.261 --> 27:32.062
Because I'm afraid to go, okay?

27:32.097 --> 27:34.815
I just thought it'd be easier
to blame it on you.

27:34.849 --> 27:37.818
Well, you've never been afraid
of anything in your life.

27:37.852 --> 27:39.136
Because my life has been
pretty sheltered.

27:39.154 --> 27:41.071
Because you built that
ramp that I just rolled down

27:41.106 --> 27:42.573
so I could get
in the living room.

27:42.607 --> 27:44.408
Because you converted the den
into my bedroom

27:44.442 --> 27:46.143
so I didn't have to go upstairs.

27:46.161 --> 27:47.745
Because you built that
bathroom add-on...

27:47.779 --> 27:49.413
Artie, <i>you</i> did those things.

27:49.447 --> 27:51.915
