28:16.141 --> 28:18.776
since you were a kid.

28:18.810 --> 28:20.060
You're going.

28:21.813 --> 28:23.280
I love you.

28:23.314 --> 28:25.182
I love you, too.

28:26.401 --> 28:31.905
