faceflop like a ragdoll,

28:50.041 --> 28:52.392
at least, I don't know,

28:52.427 --> 28:53.510
try to make me laugh.

28:53.544 --> 28:54.645
You know what?

28:54.679 --> 28:56.146
You've been wrong
about me all year,

28:56.181 --> 28:58.232
and you're gonna be
wrong about me again.

29:04.022 --> 29:05.889
